# Fundi Creator — environment variables.
#
# POLICY: all env is SERVER-SIDE and injected at RUNTIME. There are NO
# `NEXT_PUBLIC_*` variables — nothing here is ever inlined into the client
# bundle. Read these only from `process.env` in a server context (server
# component, route handler, server action). A lint rule enforces this
# (packages/config/eslint/next.js); see packages/docs/features/0007.
#
# Local dev: copy to `.env.local` (gitignored) and fill in.
#   cp apps/creator/.env.example apps/creator/.env.local
# Deployed (Vercel): values come from the GitHub `dev` Environment and are
# applied as Vercel runtime env by the deploy workflow — never committed.

# Base URL of the Fundi API (server-to-server calls only). Example first var;
# not consumed yet. Local backend default below.
API_BASE_URL="http://localhost:3000"
